article.headline: Bell leads Jacksonville over NC A&T 61-45
article.linkText: Bell leads Jacksonville over NC A&T 61-45
article.story: GREENSBORO, N.C. -- David Bell tallied 16 points and 14 rebounds to carry Jacksonville to a 61-45 win over North Carolina A&T on Saturday. Kevin Norman added 12 points for Jacksonville (4-5). Destin Barnes added seven rebounds. Ronald Jackson had 10 rebounds for the Aggies (2-6). Jacksonville plays Marquette on the road on Wednesday.
